&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: black; font-size: 18pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Mj_Egypt; mso-hansi-font-family: Mj_Egypt;" lang="FA"&gt;
